{"tid":1076872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[台灣海峽=美國西岸] 不顧北京反對，美國軍艦再次穿越台灣海峽，這回還帶了海岸防衛隊 陸媒跳腳大喊「挑釁」！","createTime":"2019-03-25T07:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T07:41:50.000Z","uid":141151,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d2d61068aa81c6c714728b96c394b95ca6cd9aa7","tid":1076872,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:22:11.000Z","msg":"不顧北京反對，美國軍艦再次穿越台灣海峽，這回還帶了海岸防衛隊 陸媒跳腳大喊「挑釁」！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%8D%E9%A1%A7%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%BB%8D%E8%89%A6%E5%86%8D%E6%AC%A1%E7%A9%BF%E8%B6%8A%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD-%E9%80%99%E5%9B%9E%E9%82%84%E5%B8%B6%E4%BA%86%E6%B5%B7%E5%B2%B8%E9%98%B2%E8%A1%9B%E9%9A%8A-%E9%99%B8%E5%AA%92%E8%B7%B3%E8%85%B3%E5%A4%A7%E5%96%8A-%E6%8C%91%E9%87%81-062729395.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25BB%258D%25E8%2589%25A6%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E8%25B6%258A%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25B3%25BD-%25E9%2580%2599%25E5%259B%259E%25E9%2582%2584%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E4%25BA%2586%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25B2%25B8%25E9%2598%25B2%25E8%25A1%259B%25E9%259A%258A-%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25AA%2592%25E8%25B7%25B3%25E8%2585%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2596%258A-%25E6%258C%2591%25E9%2587%2581-062729395.html&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6WjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=031577cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%8D%E9%A1%A7%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%BB%8D%E8%89%A6%E5%86%8D%E6%AC%A1%E7%A9%BF%E8%B6%8A%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD-%E9%80%99%E5%9B%9E%E9%82%84%E5%B8%B6%E4%BA%86%E6%B5%B7%E5%B2%B8%E9%98%B2%E8%A1%9B%E9%9A%8A-%E9%99%B8%E5%AA%92%E8%B7%B3%E8%85%B3%E5%A4%A7%E5%96%8A-%E6%8C%91%E9%87%81-062729395.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年3月25日 下午2:27<br />\n<br />\n美國軍方24日發布消息，美國海軍與海岸防衛隊的兩艘軍艦在24日至25日之間穿過台灣海峽。中國官媒《環球時報》25日以「挑釁！美國軍艦再次穿越台海，還帶了一艘海警船」為題報導此事，並指出美國最近不顧北京反對，增加了軍艦穿越台灣海峽的頻率。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">此次穿越台海的兩艘美國軍艦分別為「阿利伯克級」（Arleigh Burke-class）飛彈驅逐艦「柯蒂斯．威爾伯號」（USS Curtis Wilbur）以及<span style=\"color: red;\">海岸防衛隊（US Coast Guard）巡防艦「巴索夫號」（USCGC Bertholf）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我(台灣)國防部25日證實此事，兩艘美艦24日由我國西南海域向北航經台灣海峽。國防部指出，美艦航經我國周邊海域期間，國軍依規定運用聯合情監偵全程掌握，確保區域穩定與海疆安全，期間並無異常情形，請國人放心。國軍對於美艦動態都有掌握，確保海疆安全及區域穩定，請國人放心。<br />\n<br />\n第七艦隊（Seventh Fleet）發言人多斯（Clay Doss）中校對美國有線電視新聞網（CNN）表示：「兩艘軍艦穿越台灣海峽，彰顯了美國維護印太地區（Indo-Pacific）自由與開放的決心」。<br />\n<br />\n美國軍艦此次穿越台灣海峽已經是9個月來第6次，今年第3次。上一次是2月25日，當時美軍飛彈驅逐艦「史塔森號」（USS Stethem）、補給艦「西薩．查維斯號」（USNS Cesar Chavez）依據國際法例行穿越台灣海峽。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2月26日，中國外交部發言人陸慷抗議美國軍艦通過台灣海峽。他說：「我們堅決反對美方採取的挑釁行為，這無助於台海和平穩定、無助於中美關係發展。」</span>"},{"pid":"85ca4fa7529b926d9ff48ea6db094ec464959c30","tid":1076872,"uid":3241,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:23:35.000Z","msg":"4500噸傳奇級國家安全艦<br />\n支那果堆垃圾056食屎啦"},{"pid":"6bcecf536d6f43bfa3bf1d6f1119ec3f3fa2f0e3","tid":1076872,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:34:22.000Z","msg":"打啦...."},{"pid":"271033e340dd03f34b0c1a42d3d59a4143410efd","tid":1076872,"uid":13303,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />將美軍經過嘅地方dq出去就得啦"},{"pid":"530cec6bc9ed8c92e1f99d8357acb9fcfceb3f88","tid":1076872,"uid":116198,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:36:56.000Z","msg":"內蒙古呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38437991e69b520cb79ed803dea32fd2f3920db","tid":1076872,"uid":61280,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T07:41:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 